# Sequential Acceptance-criteria Command

**Product Owner Agent Only**: Executes structured acceptance-criteria through guided sequential methodology.

## Metadata
- **Name**: acceptance-criteria
- **Description**: Sequential acceptance criteria definition process
- **Agent**: Product Owner
- **Performance**: Sequential (focused approach vs parallel streams)
- **Approach**: Interactive guidance and systematic methodology

## Overview

The `/acceptance-criteria` command enables the Product Owner to execute acceptance-criteria through:
- Sequential development with focused attention on each aspect
- Interactive guidance through acceptance-criteria components  
- Systematic methodology ensuring comprehensive coverage
- Thorough validation and refinement process
- Clear documentation with detailed rationale

## Usage

```
/acceptance-criteria
```

